nodes.text: Iced donut with chopped ettel nuts

Iced donuts with chopped ettel nuts was a type of iced donut which contained or was covered in chopped up ettel nuts. They were served on the planet Coruscant in Dex's Diner where they were made by a Crisp-E-O donut droid in a traditional Adarian style every morning. They cost 1.7 credits.
